The puppet manifests in this directory are implemented to
install a Hypertable cluster.

Proper sequence: 
1.: init_hypertable.pp  // For installing the Hypertable package, set up directories, etc.
2.: init_hypertable_data_volume.pp  // For the set up of storage element for Hypertable.
3.: init_hypertable_service.pp  // For initializing, starting the Hypertable instances.

